io.toolisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.tools.generics

Class GenericTypeWildcard

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.toolisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.tools.generics.GenericTypeWildcard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericTypeParameter

    public final class GenericTypeWildcard
extends Object
implements GenericTypeParameter
    This class represents a wildcard based type parameter.

    It may define extends and super wildcards or a pure wildcard.
